{"TopicId":62569,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to fix this broken wheel!!","CreatedByName":"Cerberus738","CreatedById":100744,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T19:58:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cerberus738","CreatedById":100744,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T19:58:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo i built a ferris wheel... part of my new project \u0022AMAZING 0G RIDES ON THE MOON!\u0022 I was testing it at KSC and managed to break a wheel that i\u0027m using as a bearing. does anyone have a suggestion on how to fix the wheel? i don\u0027t want to relaunch it plus if it breaks down again i should like to be able to fix it once it\u0027s on the moon. i know i can fix it with a kerbal on eva but....\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/n0XnIhG.png\u0022 alt=\u0022n0XnIhG.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Qn8Ucxt.png\u0022 alt=\u0022Qn8Ucxt.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eas you can see its a ways up off the ground.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-02-08T21:03:34Z\u0022 title=\u002202/08/2014 09:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 8, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Cerberus738\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mythbusters844","CreatedById":72313,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T20:01:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EKerbals can lift off with the EVA pack on the Mun. You should have no problems fixing the wheel there; just fly up and repair it. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Nice Ferris wheel by the way.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sjwt","CreatedById":9268,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T20:07:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGet a Kerbal out there, turn on \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Debug_Toolbar\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003Ethe gravity hack\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E, and away you go with your EVA pack, or fly something out there that is tall enough that you can manage to get close enough..\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cerberus738","CreatedById":100744,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T20:10:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ei always forget about their jetpacks on planets ha ha ha. what about on kerbin... i was gonna scrap it after but its kinda cool and i want to keep it now. it works with the wheel broken but it jitters and i don\u0027t want it to break anymore!! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cerberus738","CreatedById":100744,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T20:12:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sjwt\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sjwt\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EGet a Kerbal out there, turn on \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Debug_Toolbar\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003Ethe gravity hack\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E, and away you go with your EVA pack,\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENO HACKS!!! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blizzy78","CreatedById":68543,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T20:18:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBuild a crane and lift a Kerbal up there.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cerberus738","CreatedById":100744,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-08T21:02:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Eaaah! Great success!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/RLrgwhA.png\u0022 alt=\u0022RLrgwhA.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ewhere would we be without KAS \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks for the suggestions!\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-02-08T21:04:21Z\u0022 title=\u002202/08/2014 09:04  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 8, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Cerberus738\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ethanks\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cerberus738","CreatedById":100744,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T04:39:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Efor anyone that cares here it is successfully deployed on the Mun!!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/GXSx8Qm.png\u0022 alt=\u0022GXSx8Qm.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u0022that\u0027s one small step for man, one giant line for admission\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShadowDragon8685","CreatedById":65374,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T13:43:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOnly the Kerbal Space Program would spend a thousand tons of rocket fuel to put a Ferris Wheel on the Mun. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}